DROP EXTERNAL TABLE DIM_Division;

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE DIM_Division (
	[RESTRICTDIVISION] nvarchar(4000),
	[DIVISION] nvarchar(4000)
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'DataLake/Structured/Dimensions/DIM_DIVISION.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO

SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.DIM_Division
GO
